Package: university
Type: Package
Title: Match your ggplot2 plots to your university!
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew McCartney
Maintainer: Andrew McCartney <acm9q@virginia.edu>
Description: Provides scale_color() functions for ggplot2 plots based on color schemes used by various universities for branding. 
    You can style your charts for your presentation to match your university colors! 
    Code structure taken from package ggsci:
    https://github.com/road2stat/ggsci
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    scales
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
